  "stem": "<p class=\"stem_paragraph \">Some values of the linear function <span class=\"italic\">f </span>are shown in the table above. What is the value of <span class=\"math-container\"><img align=\"middle\" role=\"math\" class=\"math-img\" src=\"data:image/png;base64,\" alt=\"f of 3\"></span>?</p>\n",
